Description: CVE-2026-42011 - Fix intersecting empty permitted name constraints
 Permitted name constraints were ignored when one CA had only excluded
 constraints and permitted intersection was skipped because one
 permitted list was empty (early return in name_constraints_node_list_intersect).
 This matches upstream 1dead2faec6320aaba321eb56f20d442df192b83.
 .
